Maverick
************************************************/
// BASIC + VANILLA
 "Introduction.Maverick": "Remember to pick up after yourself, I might keep the graveyard clean but I'm no butler.$5",

// GENERIC 
 "Mon.Maverick.spring": "There's always a big fuss over that flower dancing get together.$5#$b#Never did understand it, but I've never been one for partying.$1",
 "Tue.Maverick.spring": "I wouldn't consider myself the most social person, but at least I'm generally polite to everyone.#$b#If they treat me the same...$2",
 "Wed.Maverick.spring": "You know, I have a son. Two, actually.$1#$b#You'd think they'd get along on account of them being twins.#$b#But they seem to hate each other.$2#$b#John's over in East Scarp and Roger well...He's somewhere, haven't heard from him in a while.$5",
 "Thu.Maverick.spring": "People always say that graveyard's give them the creeps.$2#$b3I never felt that way, it's peaceful here.$1#$b#There's nothing to fear here, all the spirit's are resting.$1",
 "Fri.Maverick.spring": "I wish there was a temple of Yoba in Pelican Town.#$b#There's that altar at the shop but it's pretty pathetic in comparison to a real house of worship.",
 "Sat.Maverick.spring": "Watch your step.$5#$b#It's pretty bad karma to go stomping over gravesites.#$e#I'm being serious, that's a quick way to wake up a spirit.$2",
 "Sun.Maverick.spring": "I know I really should be making friends and putting myself out there.#$b#But frankly, I like being alone.$1#$e#Don't like dating either, it's pretty uncomfortable for me. That's why my wife and I split actually, we both are happier now.$1",
 "Mon.Maverick.summer": "If you see any litter around, be a friend and pick it up would you?$2#$b#I know it's my job, but everyone should want a clean planet yeah?",
 "Tue.Maverick.summer": "I don't spend all my time cleaning the graveyard up you know.#$b#I like to hike and fish in my free time too.$1#$e#Keeping this property clean is a full time job though, always something needing done.$1",
 "Wed.Maverick.summer": "It's hot today, but I don't mind it.#$b#I always liked the heat, makes my bones feel better then the cold.$1#$e#You sure are a talkative type huh...$1",
 "Thu.Maverick.summer.": "If you come on a rainy day, you can see the spirits of the graveyard wandering.#$b#It's safe here, but something about the rain makes the restless more active.$2",
 "Fri.Maverick.summer": "There's always property for sell here.#$b#Cause it's next to a graveyard it's real cheap too.$1#$b#People rather not deal with the dead I guess.",
 "Sat.Maverick.summer": "I love animals you know, I used to want to own a ranch and everything.#$b#But it's okay I enjoy what I do.$1#$e#You're looking pretty red in the face, maybe you should find some shade.$2",
 "Sun.Maverick.summer": "I usually keep my home locked up, never know who will end up being a thief.$5",
 "Mon.Maverick.fall": "Love is always in the air isn't it?#$b#Well I'm always seeing it.$1#$b#You see it in everything really, if you just pay attention.$2",
 "Tue.Maverick.fall": "Wait...close your eyes and listen very carefully.#$b#You hear that? I keep hearing some kind of bird sound.#$b#I think it's a bird, sounds sort of weird though.",
 "Wed.Maverick.fall": "It' pretty common to see people hiding who they really are.#$b#But it's never fooled me, I can see through the mask people wear.",
 "Thu.Maverick.fall": "Overheard Alex today saying I'm a 'creepy dude'.$2#$b#I guess a lot of people think that on account of my work.#$b#But you know, someone has to do it.$1",
 "Fri.Maverick.fall": "My whole family is real religious, think that's why I love my work so much.#$b#I feel like I'm serving Yoba in my own way.",
 "Sat.Maverick.fall": "Spirit's Eve is just around the corner.#$b#I usually drop off some candy before the festival starts, not really into sticking around though.$1",
 "Sun.Maverick.fall": "I don't go to the saloon at all.#$b#I feel maybe I should, just to make some friends but I don't know.#$b#Never been too good at making friends.$1",
 "Mon.Maverick.winter": "Winter is the easiest time of the year, no ones outside making any messes.$1#$b#Miss being warm though.",
 "Tue.Maverick.winter": "Passerby Cemetery was founded by the guild a very long time ago. Somewhere in the woods there's even an older graveyard, too.",
 "Wed.Maverick.winter": "Some of the grave markers are ridiculous, but at least some people have a decent sense of humor.$1",
 "Thu.Maverick.winter": "The morgue is under my house, in my basement.#$b#I'm happy it's been a while since I've had to use it.",
 "Fri.Maverick.winter": "I used to watch a lot of cartoons as a kid, been thinking about those shows a lot these days.#$b#Maybe I could watch a few for old times sake.$1",
 "Sat.Maverick.winter": "I've been attempting to read a little bit of a book every night.#$b#But I really have no clue how to focus on reading for longer then five mintues.$1",
 "Sun.Maverick.winter": "I heard they found a new type of rat in East Scarp, John keeps bitchin about it stealing his stuff.$1#$b#Pretty funny to me.$1",


